---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 lg:px-8 py-16 lg:py-24">
        <div class="prose prose-base lg:prose-lg text-base-content max-w-none">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-black tracking-tighter text-primary mb-8">
                Terms of Use
            </h1>
            <p class="text-sm opacity-70 mb-8">
                Last Updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString()}
            </p>

            <p>
                Welcome to Barq Telecommunication Pvt Ltd. By accessing our
                website, purchasing our equipment, or using our fiber and
                wireless networking services, you agree to comply with and be
                bound by the following terms and conditions.
            </p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">1. Service Provision</h2>
            <p>
                Barq provides internet connectivity (Fiber/Wireless) and
                telecommunications equipment. Service availability, speeds, and
                quality may vary based on geographic location, network
                congestion, and environmental factors. We reserve the right to
                perform network maintenance which may result in temporary
                downtime.
            </p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">
                2. Acceptable Use Policy (AUP)
            </h2>
            <p>
                Our network must not be used to transmit, distribute, or store
                material that violates any applicable law. Prohibited activities
                include, but are not limited to:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>Spamming or sending unsolicited bulk communications.</li>
                <li>
                    Hacking, bypassing security protocols, or distributing
                    malware.
                </li>
                <li>
                    Copyright infringement or unauthorized sharing of protected
                    intellectual property.
                </li>
            </ul>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">
                3. Billing and Subscriptions
            </h2>
            <p>
                All subscription charges must be paid by the due date. Failure
                to settle outstanding invoices may result in the suspension or
                termination of your telecommunication services. Equipment
                remains the property of Barq unless fully purchased as part of a
                specific agreement.
            </p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">
                4. Limitation of Liability
            </h2>
            <p>
                Barq Telecommunication shall not be liable for any indirect,
                incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages, or any
                loss of profits or revenues arising from the use or inability to
                use our services.
            </p>

            <div class="mt-12 p-6 bg-base-200 rounded-xl">
                <p class="font-bold m-0">Questions regarding these terms?</p>
                <p class="text-sm mt-2 mb-0">
                    Please visit our <a
                        href="/contact"
                        class="text-primary hover:underline">Contact Us</a
                    > page or speak to <a
                        href="/customer-care"
                        class="text-primary hover:underline">Customer Care</a
                    >.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
